## <a id="reqs"></a>Requirements

Kubernetes Service Manager for PCF has the following requirements:

* A container registry like [Harbor](https://network.pivotal.io/products/harbor-container-registry)
  is needed to manage images in disconnected environments (and advisable for any production deployments).
* [Docker](https://www.docker.com/)
* The [PKS CLI](https://docs.pivotal.io/runtimes/pks/cli/index.html)

## <a id="limitations"></a>Limitations

* Dedicated-instances created by the Kubernetes Service Manager for PCF provision
  an IaaS load balancer for ingress into each instance.

